  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2006-09-28",
    "date": "2006-11-28T16:26:11Z",
    "text": "Amends the Hobby Protection Act to declare as an unlawful, unfair, and deceptive act the manufacture in the United States, or the importation into the United States, for introduction or distribution into commerce of any imitation Civil War item which is not plainly and permanently marked \"copy\" or \"facsimile.\"\n\nRequires the Federal Trade Commission to prescribe rules relating to such items that are substantially similar to the rules prescribed by the Commission relating to imitation numismatic items."
